	3 ‘the ecliptic.’ 1) Taittirīya Brāhmaṇa, i. 7, 6, 6; 
Pañcaviṃśa Brāhmaṇa, xxv. 12, 3; 
Śatapatha Brāhmaṇa, v. 3, 1, 2. 2) Über den Rājasūya, 48, 2. 3) Vedische Mythologie, 3, 79, 80.

अर्यल
अर्यल
 — Those at whose snake feast the Gṛhapati was Aryala, 
