ii. 1, 2, 4; Taittirīya Āraṇyaka, i. 11, 2. 
Cf. Hillebrandt, Vedische Mythologie, 3, 
422. 4) Cf. Macdonell, Vedic Mythology, 
p. 144 (D).

ऋक्ष
2. Ṛkṣa is the name of a patron mentioned in one verse of a 
