ऋग्वेद
ऋग्-वेद,
 the formal name of the collection of Ṛcs, first 
appears in the Brāhmaṇas,
	1 and thereafter frequently in the 
Āraṇyakas
	2 and Upaniṣads.
	3 1) Aitareya Brāhmaṇa, i. 32, and 
