Lāṭyāyana Śrauta Sūtra, viii. 11, 18. 5) Śatapatha Brāhmaṇa, v. 5, 2, 3. 5. 6) Taittirīya Brāhmaṇa, 1. 8, 4. 1, 2. 7) Jaiminīya Brāhmaṇa, ii. 78; Jaimi
nīya Upaniṣad Brāhmaṇa, iii. 30, 6; 
iv. 6, 2; Bṛhadāraṇyaka Upaniṣad, 
iii. 1, 1; 9, 20, etc. 8) Indische Studien, 3, 470; Indian 
