also Kṛṣṇājina. 1) Taittirīya Saṃhitā, v. 2, 6, 5; 
vi. 1, 3, 1; Śatapatha Brāhmaṇa, i. 1, 
4, 1; iii. 2, 1, 28. So kṛṣṇa-viṣāṇā, 
