3, 7. See also the Aśvamedha passages, 
Maitrāyaṇī Saṃhitā, iii. 14, 17; Vāja
saneyi Saṃhitā, xxiv. 36 (cf. ii. 1). 2) Rv. x. 94, 5; Av. xi. 2, 2; Śāṅkhāyana Āraṇyaka, xii. 27.

