	6 
suggests connexion with the Pāli palāsāda, ‘rhinoceros.’ 1) St. Petersburg Dictionary, s.v. 2) x. 86, 18. 3) vi. 72, 2; xx. 131, 22. 4) Maitrāyaṇī Saṃhitā, iii. 14, 10; 
