ii. 1, 1, 5: v. 1, 1, 3; 2, 6. 19) Op. cit., 77, 78. 20) xi, 2, 24. 25, compared with xii. 1, 
40, 51. 21) Hymns of the Atharvaveda, 631. 22) Translation of the Atharvaveda, 
