330. 6) Rv. iv. 42, 8. 9. 7) Rv. v. 33, 8; viii. 19, 36. 8) Rv. vii. 19, 3. 9) Rv. iv. 42, 8. 9, with Sāyaṇa's 
note; Muir, Sanskrit Texts, 1^2, 266, 267. 10) Die Sagenstoffe des Ṛgveda, 96-102. 11) xiii. 5, 4, 5. 12) vii. 18. Cf. also the reference to 
a Pūru defeat in vii. 8, 4. 13) xiii. 5, 4, 5. Cf. Ikṣvāku, Tryaruṇa, 
