पूर्णमास
पूर्ण-मास
 denotes the full moon and the festival of that 
day, occurring frequently in the later Saṃhitās.
	1 Cf. Māsa. 1) Taittirīya Saṃhitā, i. 6, 7, 2; ii. 2, 
10, 2; 5, 4, 1; iii. 4, 4, 1; vii. 4, 8, 1; 
Taittirīya Brāhmaṇa, i. 2, 1, 14; iii. 5, 
