पूर्त
पूर्त,
 
	1 or Pūrti,
	2 occurs in the Rigveda and later denoting 
the reward to the priest for his services. Cf. Dakṣiṇā. 1) Rv. vi. 16, 18; viii. 46, 21; Av. 
vi. 123, 5; ix. 5, 13; 6, 31; Vājasaneyi 
Saṃhitā, xviii. 64; Aitareya Brāhmaṇa, 
