Sūtra, xv. 14, 23, etc. 2) Rv. i. 37, 2; 39, 6; 64, 8; 85, 4, 5; 
ii. 34, 3; 36, 2; iii. 26, 4; v. 55, 6; 
58, 6; 60, 2; i. 162, 21. 3) On Vājasaneyi Saṃhitā, ii. 16. 4) St. Petersburg Dictionary, s.v. He 
had earlier (ibid., 1, 1091) been inclined 
to follow the usual interpretation given 
by Sāyaṇa on Rv. i. 37, 2, etc., which 
