796. Weber is inclined to detect a 
Babylonian origin of Maṇi (cf. Manā), 
but the evidence is not convincing.

मणिक
मणिक
 in the late Adbhuta Brāhmaṇa
	1 and the Sūtras
	2 
denotes a large ‘water bottle.’ 1) Weber, Omina und Portenta, 316. 2) Āśvalāyana Gṛhya Sūtra, ii. 9, 3; 
iv. 6, 4; Gobhila Gṛhya Sūtra, i. 1, 26; 
iii. 9, 6. 7, etc.; Sāṅkhāyana Gṛhya 
