	3 as the name of a Bharadvāja. 1) vi. 10, 2. Cf. Mahābhārata, i. 4179 
et seq. 2) Zeitschrift der Deutschen Morgen- 
lāndischen Gesellschaft, 42, 212. 3) vi. 50, 15, where the reading of the 
