and the Addenda of that work. On 
the accentuation of the name, see 
Vārttika 2 on Pāṇini, vi. 2, 106. 2) x. 75, 5. 3) Zur Litteratur und Geschichte des 
Weda, 138 et seq. 4) Altindisches Leben, 11, 12. 5) Translation of the Rigveda, 3, 
200.

