name of a Vedic text in the Rigveda Gṛhya Sūtras.
	1 1) Āśvalāyana Gṛhya Sūtra, iii. 4, 4; 
Mahākauṣītaki, the teacher, in Śāṅkh
āyana Gṛhya Sūtra, iv. 10; vi. 1, etc. 
Cf. Oldenberg, Sacred Books of the East, 
