महा-पथ
 in the Brāhmaṇas
	1 denotes the ‘high road’ 
between two villages. 1) Aitareya Brāhmaṇa, iv. 17, 8; Chāndogya Upaniṣad, viii. 6, 2. Cf. Weber, 
Indische Studien, 1, 271, n.

महापुर
महा-पुर
 in the Yajurveda Saṃhitās
	1 and the Brāhmaṇas
