महिदासऐतरेय
महि-दास ऐतरेय
 (‘descendant of Itara or Itarā’) is the 
name of the sage from whom the Aitareya Brāhmaṇa and 
Āraṇyaka take their names. He is several times referred to in 
the Aitareya Āraṇyaka,
	1 but not as its author. He is credited 
with a life of 116 years in the Chāndogya Upaniṣad
	2 and the 
Jaiminīya Upaniṣad Brāhmaṇa
