मांसौदन
मांसौदन
 denotes in the Śatapatha Brāhmaṇa
	1 a dish 
consisting of ‘meat cooked with rice.’ 1) xi. 5, 7, 5; Bṛhadāraṇyaka Upaniṣad, vi. 4, 18; Śāṅkhāyana Āraṇyaka, 
xii. 8.

