मागध-देशीय,
 ‘belonging to the district of Magadha,’ is 
the description in the Sūtras
	1 of a Brahmin of Magadha. 1) Kātyāyana Śrauta Sūtra, xxii. 4, 22; Lāṭyāyana Śrauta Sūtra, viii. 6, 28.

