माण्डवी
माण्डवी,
 ‘female descendant of Maṇḍu,’ occurs in the 
name of a teacher, Vātsī-māṇḍavī-putra, in the Bṛhadāraṇyaka 
Upaniṣad (vi. 4, 30 Mādhyaṃdina).

