वि-चृत्
 in the dual is found in three passages of the Atharva
veda,
	1 where Roth
	2 sees in the term the name of two stars, 
while in the Taittirīya Saṃhitā
	3 he thinks they mean the 
Nakṣatra called Mūla. There can, however, be no doubt that 
